name: Rent
tagline: Rent is a minimalist approach to Blender's GUI engine built upon an Eclipse foundation
body:
### Welcome to Rent; the minimalist Blender-based GUI Engine.
Rent is a component of various applications, together creating a dynamic graphic environment. It uses C++, PHP, Eclipse and several other IDE/compilers. 

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.
